node.text:
Make sure to tune into today’s stories for a tour of the exterior, interior and kitchen of our new home. Today I spent a little bit of time covering our @leaffilter gutter system as now is the perfect time to install gutter covers to be ready for fall and not worry about falling leaves or debris clogging you gutters.
 
In our case we installed gutters, downspouts and covers all at the same time, but LeafFilter Gutter Protection can be installed on top of your existing gutters and once they are in place you will never have to worry about cleaning your gutters, having ugly water stains on siding, rotting fascia, or potential foundation damage caused by excessive rainwater not diverted away from your home.
 
Remember that your gutters and downspouts are completely useless if they’re clogged so having high quality gutter covers is one of THE most important parts of your home’s drainage system.
 
Thank you @leaffilter for sponsoring this post. #leaffilter #gutterprotection #newconstruction #newbuild #stuccohouse #portico #customhome #blackandwhiteexterior #blackgutters #homebuilding
